609
00:39:20,255 --> 00:39:21,855
To by sme mali.

610
00:39:23,465 --> 00:39:24,665
Čo ďalej?

611
00:39:25,465 --> 00:39:26,795
Počkáme.

612
00:39:26,864 --> 00:39:29,335
Narobili sme dostatok dymu,

613
00:39:29,335 --> 00:39:34,134
takže teraz počkáme,
až vykukne z jaskyne, aby sa nadýchol.

614
00:39:41,315 --> 00:39:44,285
Lee Do Jin. Čo by ten mohol chcieť?

615
00:39:45,185 --> 00:39:46,884
