616
00:39:54,054 --> 00:39:55,464
Máš sa dobre?

617
00:40:01,364 --> 00:40:02,804
To je všetko?

618
00:40:03,704 --> 00:40:08,274
Zavoláte niekomu,
koho ste osobne vyhodili,

619
00:40:11,074 --> 00:40:13,115
